```plantuml
@startuml IBM_customer-sentiment-on-seller-quality-nlu-cp4d
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor User

rectangle "Jupyter Notebook" as Notebook #lightblue

rectangle "Db2 Database" as Db2 #lightyellow
rectangle "Watson NLU" as WatsonNLU #lightgreen
rectangle "Embedded Dashboard" as Dashboard #lightpink

' Interaction between components
User --> Notebook : Launch Notebook\nand configure
Notebook --> Db2 : Load customer review data
Notebook --> WatsonNLU : Perform sentiment analysis
WatsonNLU --> Notebook : Return sentiment scores
Notebook --> Notebook : Calculate seller quality ratings
Notebook --> Dashboard : Generate data for visualization
Dashboard --> User : Display interactive dashboard

@enduml
```